01:36:10.920 --> 01:36:13.920
[Guest]: and you are being whipped and lashed and what not

01:36:13.920 --> 01:36:16.920
[Guest]: unspeakable things happening to you will I have the gumption

01:36:16.920 --> 01:36:19.920
[Guest]: to go through all that take it all

