01:36:25.920 --> 01:36:28.920
[Guest]: no I don't think so if I know

01:36:28.920 --> 01:36:31.920
[Guest]: if I have been told that ok if you write a letter

01:36:31.920 --> 01:36:34.920
[Guest]: you might get a way out I will

01:36:34.920 --> 01:36:37.920
[Guest]: I will not think about at that point in time I will not think

01:36:37.920 --> 01:36:40.920
