01:36:43.920 --> 01:36:46.920
[Guest]: I will just think I want to escape this pain

01:36:46.920 --> 01:36:49.920
[Guest]: so I don't flaw him for the mercy petition

01:36:49.920 --> 01:36:52.920
[Guest]: I just flaw him for his ideas

01:36:52.920 --> 01:36:55.920
[Guest]: and I think that's like you said rightly that's more than

01:36:55.920 --> 01:36:58.920
[Guest]: enough he gives you more than enough fodder to

01:36:58.920 --> 01:37:01.920
[Guest]: criticize him and then again you have to

01:37:01.920 --> 01:37:04.920
[Guest]: also recognize that I keep saying this is a running

01:37:04.920 --> 01:37:07.920
[Guest]: motive and all kinds of historical accounts

01:37:07.920 --> 01:37:10.920
[Guest]: all kinds of historical characters that everyone has

01:37:10.920 --> 01:37:13.920
[Guest]: graced then again if you take him as a Hindutva icon he

01:37:13.920 --> 01:37:16.920
[Guest]: spoke very vocally against cow vigilantism

01:37:16.920 --> 01:37:19.920
[Guest]: he was

01:37:19.920 --> 01:37:22.920
[Guest]: like if Savarkar would have said even one statement of that

01:37:22.920 --> 01:37:25.920
[Guest]: kind today he would have been lynched or at least

01:37:25.920 --> 01:37:28.920
[Guest]: cancelled out by the right on twitter and he was extremely anti-cast

01:37:28.920 --> 01:37:31.920
[Guest]: he was extremely anti-cast and frankly

01:37:31.920 --> 01:37:34.920
[Guest]: Hindutva is also anti-cast I mean we both

01:37:34.920 --> 01:37:37.920
[Guest]: know that there is statistics to establish that

01:37:37.920 --> 01:37:40.920
[Guest]: all the caste issue that I see that's a very left wing

01:37:40.920 --> 01:37:43.920
[Guest]: kind of thing but then that's a separate discussion all together

01:37:43.920 --> 01:37:46.920
[Guest]: then Nathuram Godse was a very anti-caste figure because

01:37:46.920 --> 01:37:49.920
[Guest]: that time their ideology was we have to unite

01:37:49.920 --> 01:37:52.920
[Guest]: Hindus against a common enemy and you cannot do that

01:37:52.920 --> 01:37:55.920
[Guest]: in a country where only 5% is

01:37:55.920 --> 01:37:58.920
[Guest]: upper caste or 3% definitely not more than

01:37:58.920 --> 01:38:01.920
[Guest]: 5% so in a country with less than 5%

01:38:01.920 --> 01:38:04.920
[Guest]: upper caste you cannot antagonize lower caste

01:38:04.920 --> 01:38:07.920
[Guest]: because you are lower you can't do that so they were very

01:38:07.920 --> 01:38:10.920
[Guest]: practical in that sense now deep within

01:38:10.920 --> 01:38:13.920
[Guest]: in their heads were they casteist

01:38:13.920 --> 01:38:16.920
[Guest]: I wouldn't know you wouldn't know but then for political

01:38:16.920 --> 01:38:19.920
[Guest]: reasons they at least made sure they did a very good job of

01:38:19.920 --> 01:38:22.920
[Amit Varma]: showing that they were for all Hindus and the thing to remember

01:38:22.920 --> 01:38:25.920
[Amit Varma]: is that as we were discussing during lunch that more

01:38:25.920 --> 01:38:28.920
[Amit Varma]: there are people online who will claim to speak for Dalits while

01:38:28.920 --> 01:38:31.920
[Amit Varma]: being savarna themselves see even I am throwing a label around who will

01:38:31.920 --> 01:38:34.920
[Amit Varma]: claim to speak for Dalits but my point is the Dalits can speak for

01:38:34.920 --> 01:38:37.920
[Amit Varma]: themselves and we know how they have spoken in both 2014

01:38:37.920 --> 01:38:40.920
[Amit Varma]: and 2019 more Dalits voted for the BJP than

01:38:40.920 --> 01:38:43.920
[Amit Varma]: any other party this is something even Jignesh Mewani

01:38:43.920 --> 01:38:46.920
[Amit Varma]: sort of lamented after he saw the results in Gujarat

01:38:46.920 --> 01:38:49.920
[Amit Varma]: and how the Dalits there voted right that they seem

01:38:49.920 --> 01:38:52.920
[Amit Varma]: to prefer the BJP and the reason they seem to prefer the BJP

01:38:52.920 --> 01:38:55.920
[Amit Varma]: is because they don't want to be reduced to that identity of being a Dalit

01:38:55.920 --> 01:38:58.920
[Amit Varma]: and a victim and they see themselves as part of the

01:38:58.920 --> 01:39:01.920
[Amit Varma]: larger Hindu vote now in a sense for me that larger

01:39:01.920 --> 01:39:04.920
[Amit Varma]: identity is also toxic because you are othering the Muslims

01:39:04.920 --> 01:39:07.920
[Amit Varma]: it's all completely messed up but the point is that

01:39:07.920 --> 01:39:10.920
[Amit Varma]: you can't simply put people in boxes and there

01:39:10.920 --> 01:39:13.920
[Amit Varma]: I mean I agree that both the Savarkar and the RSS

01:39:13.920 --> 01:39:16.920
[Amit Varma]: I mean if you look at the RSS as an organization there is a clear

01:39:16.920 --> 01:39:19.920
[Guest]: caste bias in the office bearers but in terms

01:39:19.920 --> 01:39:22.920
[Amit Varma]: of how they have approached their social work

01:39:22.920 --> 01:39:25.920
[Amit Varma]: or in terms of how the BJP you know under

01:39:25.920 --> 01:39:28.920
[Amit Varma]: Amit Shah for example in 2014 the way they

01:39:28.920 --> 01:39:31.920
[Amit Varma]: reconfigured the caste politics of UP where

01:39:31.920 --> 01:39:34.920
[Amit Varma]: they got the non Jatav Dalits on their side playing to

01:39:34.920 --> 01:39:37.920
[Amit Varma]: politics of resentment where they got the non Yadav OBCs

01:39:37.920 --> 01:39:40.920
[Amit Varma]: on their side again playing to politics of resentment

01:39:40.920 --> 01:39:43.920
[Amit Varma]: masterfully political and another kind of false

01:39:43.920 --> 01:39:46.920
[Amit Varma]: narrative that somehow that particular party is for the caste

01:39:46.920 --> 01:39:49.920
[Amit Varma]: system they are against Muslims yes they are against women also

01:39:49.920 --> 01:39:52.920
[Amit Varma]: I would say not in so many words but it's

01:39:52.920 --> 01:39:55.920
[Amit Varma]: really an anti-woman party and they are scared of women and you can see

01:39:55.920 --> 01:39:58.920
[Amit Varma]: that but it's not casteist. It's not

01:39:58.920 --> 01:40:01.920
[Guest]: and they have not been casteist since at least the

