[Guest]: they were making oil out of

03:02:49.920 --> 03:02:52.920
[Guest]: sesame seeds as early as Indus Valley Civilization

03:02:52.920 --> 03:02:55.920
[Guest]: they were doing that and they were exporting oil

03:02:55.920 --> 03:02:58.920
[Guest]: they were exporting sesame oil to

03:02:58.920 --> 03:03:01.920
[Guest]: Sumer and Mesopotamia all those kind of places

03:03:01.920 --> 03:03:04.920
[Amit Varma]: so for those people who think sesame oil is used

